{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ed2d37b4b9","title":"“党委：不要官僚下去了”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84905a359c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"11ba6247c1","name":"任筠霞"},{"id":"44cfe26f22","name":"陈淑清"},{"id":"aa8f959c5c","name":"张兰珍"},{"id":"bb4131e243","name":"上海第一师范学院班"},{"id":"cc0dc63834","name":"王玉琴"},{"id":"efc188aa3e","name":"施考华"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b686785548","type":"title","text":"“党委：不要官僚下去了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"07f7510e98","type":"authors","text":"上海第一师范学院班施考华王玉琴陈淑清任筠霞张兰珍","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"0d9c6295a6","type":"paragraph","text":"还给我们不可追回的时间！！！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"d283c008c7","type":"paragraph","text":"“专科不专”这已经成为专科同学的“共鸣”这趋向不能使我们理解，将来，我们当语文教师呢？还是当政治教师？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"d8c71d1a18","type":"paragraph","text":"专科学习时间已很短，而院方却把培养助教的任务放在我们身上，更不应该是以我们21、22二班作为助教的实验班，使我们二班都成了科学院的“兔子”“洋老鼠”。试问：招专修科的目的是为了培养助教呢？还是培养中学教员？为了对祖国负责，我们速快要求，把专修科改为本科！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"5f84666b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"党委：不要官僚下去了，赶快答应我们的要求吧！！！(中文科22班施考华 王玉琴 陈淑清 任筠霞 张兰珍)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"},{"id":"7ba2458cd1","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《鸣放言论选集》（上海第一师范学院，1957）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9"}],"page":{"id":"a8900265b7","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ed2d37b4b9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}